subject: Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Jennifer O’Neill and Makayla Epps combined for 22 second-half points, and the No. 13 Kentucky women topped No. 2 South Carolina, denying the Gamecocks an unbeaten season in Southeastern Conference play.
